%S A116116 21,30,902406,959721,6040059046,6242406405,9842410005,9900249006,
%T A116116 15033519988494,17250863148969,22499666270469,27632040031654,
%U A116116 34182546327286,37487353123861,52213551379230,74230108225630
%N A116116 Numbers k such that k concatenated with k-6 gives the product of two numbers which differ by 2.
%C A116116 If k-6 has d digits, the concatenation is k//k-6 = 10^d*k+k-6 = m*(m+2), therefore k//k-9 = 10^d*k+k-9 = (m-1)*(m+3), so there is a large overlap or equality with A116096. Also k//k-5 = 10^d*k+k-5 = (m+1)^2, so there is a large overlap or equality with A115433. - _R. J. Mathar_, May 22 2026
%e A116116 9900249006//9900249000 = 9949999500 * 9949999502, where // denotes concatenation.
%Y A116116 Cf. A116102, A116115, A115431, A115433, A116121, A116247.
%K A116116 nonn,base,more,changed
%O A116116 1,1
